        "richtext_6L8BQG": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "richtext": "<p>Six generations of stubborn, competitive growers and one equally spirited winemaker – that’s the Oliver family.<br/><br/>Living smack bang in the middle of McLaren Vale, the family flourish on producing perfect parcels of fruit on their 100 hectare ‘Taranga’ property.<br/><br/>Their collection of small batch, handcrafted, Oliver’s Taranga wines speak of both the variety and vintage, capturing a time and place, while continuing to document the family’s ongoing 185 year relationship with the land.</p>",
            "id": "",
            "class": ""
          }
        },
